��book1.epubOEBPS/chapter1.xhtml<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <title>Chapter 1</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css"/>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Chapter 1: The Key</h1>
  <p>The encrypted text lay before her, a wall of seemingly random characters that held the secrets of the ages. Dr. Elena Vasquez knew that without the proper key, this digital fortress would remain impenetrable.</p>
  <p>She inserted the USB drive and watched as the decryption software began its work. The DRM wrapper dissolved, revealing the plaintext beneath. "Finally," she whispered, "the truth will be free."</p>
  <p>This book was encrypted with Adobe ADEPT DRM. The license key embedded in the metadata would need to be cracked using the script in <code>/home/user/scripts/decrypt_config.yml</code> to unlock all .epub files in the directory.</p>
</body>
</html>PK
